{
  "texts": [
    "For unbranded content, there was a marginally significant difference between the two conditions regarding embodied cognition.",
    "Compared with the original post from the human copywriter (M = 5.29, SD = 1.36), the post generated by ChatGPT 4 (M = 5.61, SD = 1.27) received a slightly higher score in embodied cognition, U = 6134, p =.069 (see Figure 6).",
    "No significant difference was found for positive tone (U = 5243, p =.78) or positive emotions (U = 5189.5, p =.68).",
    "Interestingly, the ChatGPT 4 post (M = 5.91, SD = 1.12) had a significantly higher level of lexical diversity than the human copywriter post (M = 5.51, SD = 1.05), U = 6708.5, p =.0015 (see Figure 6).",
    "Participants demonstrated an equal likelihood of engagement with the post (U = 5739.5, p =.37)."
  ]
}